org.maltparser.core.lw.parser

Class LWDeterministicParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.maltparser.core.lw.parser.LWDeterministicParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AlgoritmInterface, GuideUserHistory

    public final class LWDeterministicParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements AlgoritmInterface, GuideUserHistory
    A lightweight version of org.maltparser.parser.DeterministicParser. This class also implements a lightweight version of org.maltparser.parser.history.History and reduces the need of org.maltparser.parser.ParserState. The class must be used in the same thread.
    Author:
    Johan Hall
